    <div class="documentTop">        
        
        <h1>EEA/EFTA Section, including the EEA Secretariat</h1>
        
        <div class="pageDescription"><p>General matters related to EEA cooperation and the implementation of the EEA Agreement. The EEA High-level Coordinating Committee, the Storting’s EEA Consultative Committee, the EEA Joint Committee and the EEA Council. Implementation of regulations, directives, etc. Matters related to the Internal Market that fall outside the scope of the EEA Agreement. Translation of EC legislation to Norwegian. General EFTA matters and coordination within the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of EFTA third-country cooperation. The EFTA Committee of Members of Parliament and the EEA Joint Parliamentary Committee.</p>
</div>        
